<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>网络拓扑</h3>
    <span class="status-badge" id="nt-status-badge">加载中...</span>
    <a href="/topology-editor/" class="btn btn-sm" style="margin-left:auto">编辑拓扑</a>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div id="nt-diagram" class="nt-diagram">
      <div class="nt-loading">加载网络拓扑...</div>
    </div>
    <div class="nt-legend">
      <span class="nt-legend-item" title="节点运行正常"><span class="nt-dot nt-dot-green"></span> 正常</span>
      <span class="nt-legend-item" title="节点异常或服务中断"><span class="nt-dot nt-dot-red"></span> 异常</span>
      <span class="nt-legend-item" title="状态未知或未获取到数据"><span class="nt-dot nt-dot-gray"></span> 未知</span>
      <span class="nt-legend-sep">|</span>
      <span class="nt-legend-item" title="链路状态未检测"><span class="nt-line-sample nt-line-gray"></span> 未检测</span>
      <span class="nt-legend-item" title="链路正常可达"><span class="nt-line-sample nt-line-green"></span> 在线</span>
      <span class="nt-legend-item" title="链路中断或异常"><span class="nt-line-sample nt-line-red"></span> 异常</span>
      <span class="nt-legend-sep">|</span>
      <span class="nt-legend-item" title="左列：公网访问（Internet → CF CDN → CF Tunnel → N150）；右列：局域网访问（手机/电脑 → 路由器 → UFW → N150）"><span class="nt-line-sample"></span> 实线：实际网络链路</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>流量路径说明</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <table class="data-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>访问方式</th><th>路径</th><th>说明</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>公网（域名访问）</td><td>Internet → CF CDN → CF Tunnel → N150</td><td>外部用户访问域名，经 Cloudflare CDN + Tunnel 到达 N150，<strong>不经过家庭网络</strong></td></tr>
        <tr><td>局域网（IP 直连）</td><td>手机/电脑 → 路由器 → UFW → N150</td><td>同局域网下通过 N150 内网 IP 直接访问服务</td></tr>
        <tr><td>家庭网络出口</td><td>N150 → 路由器 → 光猫 → ISP → Internet</td><td>N150 主动出站到公网（建立 CF Tunnel、系统更新等）</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="/js/network-topology.js?v=<%= version %>" defer></script>
